metadata.name: JEZEBEL'S CHARMS
metadata.description:
This is an experiment. 

We are all subjects and participants. We are also observers. 

This is an experiment. It comes in parts conceived yet and not yet.

The parts are connected. 

Do not forget. Do not fear. You are the experimenter, the test subject and the observer. 

It starts and provokes naked. It ends, horrifies and screams and is not naked. In between are shades of noir. 

This is an experiment. Sometimes numbers, some other times names at will. No text but this. All single editions. Starting on Athena Novo's SUPERNATURAL smart contract on Manifold. Ending here there and everywhere.

This is an experiment and your actions may have consequence if time is reversible.
